  "3329220": {
    "name": "Yet Another Climbing Game",
    "steam_appid": 3329220,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/078dc0123330a6813f828b04f29eb58a.avif?t=1767970094\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《又一个攀登游戏》是一场艰苦的攀登，是对决心的痛苦的扭曲致敬。你用一个笨拙的机械师引导你的登山者，以不精确的精度向上攀爬。这就是全部了。只要坚持，你可能会发现自己飞翔、跌倒，有时甚至命悬一线。巨大的谜团和苦乐参半的奖励等待着那些足够勇敢（或愚蠢）到达顶峰的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/369a39096ae90d9a94e4e7edd4ab6f23.poster.avif?t=1767970094\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/369a39096ae90d9a94e4e7edd4ab6f23.webm?t=1767970094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/369a39096ae90d9a94e4e7edd4ab6f23.mp4?t=1767970094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引用我的灵感：  <br><i>“只有热爱痛苦的人才能达到顶峰，因为没有其他方法。”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将使用一个简单但精确的控制系统来拖拽自己，该系统似乎是专门为测试你的耐心而设计的。每一次抓握、每一次挥杆、每一次滑倒都会让你质疑自己的选择。有了足够的韧性，你可能会找到上升的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/035830ac277342aa9943fc2afaeb97ae.avif?t=1767970094\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一次又一次地失去进步。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于少数到达顶峰的人来说，一些奇怪的事情正在等待着他们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/667351a8855687799436848a47d945aa.poster.avif?t=1767970094\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/667351a8855687799436848a47d945aa.webm?t=1767970094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/667351a8855687799436848a47d945aa.mp4?t=1767970094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
